user.bio: Here's to alcohol: the cause of, and solution to, all of life's problems!
Paris-based Beer Traveller from Scotland. Love Brett, IPAs, Sours, Belgian Beer. Keen on special occasion dark beers.
I try lots of beer & judge tough. Don't take it personally. Stouts, Barleywines & Bottleshares. Boycott Collective Arts!
